title: Lynda.com - Insights on Graphic Design with Sean Adams
description:
Lynda.com - Insights on Graphic Design with Sean Adams
32m 14s Beginner Upload in Jul 20, 2014 by 2boweb

Viewers: 5,321 in 93 countries Watching now: 1

Sean Adams is one of the most celebrated designers of our time. He also is cofounder of the firm AdamsMorioka, a professor at the Art Center College of Design, and the national president of AIGA. In this interview, Sean shares his sources of inspiration and his advice for new designers on portfolios and breaking into the industry, and discusses the role technology and social media play in a designer's life.
